---
title: Tagine-Style Apricot Chicken with Couscous & Almonds
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve enlisted the help of a lively glaze made with apricot sauce: it coats each bite of tender chicken breast
in sticky stone-fruit sweetness and even tastes great drizzled over the robust roast veggie and couscous. Go for your life!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
